page.name: BioBeasts Escape!
page.description: BioBeasts are trying to escape Frysteland through inter-dimensional portals! Can you find and save them before Alydriah and her minions capture them and find new samples?

properties.complete: You defeated Alydriah and saved the BioBeasts that managed to make it through the portal! Hopefully, her guards didn't take anything else back to Frysteland!
